  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "marching-squares",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/marching-squares/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.91,
      "size": 30528,
      "text": "地图上那一圈圈的等高线，是怎么从高度数据里画出来的？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "marching-squares",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/marching-squares/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32256,
      "text": "我们手里只有一张离散的数值网格，每个格点记录一个高度。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "marching-squares",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/marching-squares/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.96,
      "size": 31392,
      "text": "行进方块算法，就能把这些散点连成平滑的等高线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "marching-squares",
      "section_id": "sample",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "sample-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/marching-squares/xiaoxiao/sample-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32256,
      "text": "先把整个区域切成一个个小方格，这就是标量场网格。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "marching-squares",
      "section_id": "sample",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "sample-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/marching-squares/xiaoxiao/sample-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.52,
      "size": 24336,
      "text": "每个格点的值，可以想成那一点的海拔高度。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "marching-squares",
      "section_id": "sample",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "sample-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/marching-squares/xiaoxiao/sample-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.08,
      "size": 33264,
      "text": "我们设定一个阈值，比如海拔一千米，要画出这条高度线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "marching-squares",
      "section_id": "lookup",
      "line_id": "case-1",
      "filename": "lookup-case-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/marching-squares/xiaoxiao/lookup-case-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.93,
      "size": 30816,
      "text": "看每个方格的四个角，比阈值高记作一，低记作零。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "marching-squares",
      "section_id": "lookup",
      "line_id": "case-2",
      "filename": "lookup-case-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/marching-squares/xiaoxiao/lookup-case-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.13,
      "size": 34128,
      "text": "四个角各是零或一，一共有二的四次方，也就是十六种组合。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "marching-squares",
      "section_id": "lookup",
      "line_id": "case-3",
      "filename": "lookup-case-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/marching-squares/xiaoxiao/lookup-case-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.17,
      "size": 34704,
      "text": "每种组合都对应一张查找表，直接告诉我们该连哪几条边。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "marching-squares",
      "section_id": "interp",
      "line_id": "lerp-1",
      "filename": "interp-lerp-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/marching-squares/xiaoxiao/interp-lerp-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.41,
      "size": 22608,
      "text": "等高线穿过某条边时，交点在哪里呢？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "marching-squares",
      "section_id": "interp",
      "line_id": "lerp-2",
      "filename": "interp-lerp-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/marching-squares/xiaoxiao/interp-lerp-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.51,
      "size": 40176,
      "text": "用两个端点的值做线性插值，阈值越靠近哪端，交点就越靠哪端。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "marching-squares",
      "section_id": "interp",
      "line_id": "lerp-3",
      "filename": "interp-lerp-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/marching-squares/xiaoxiao/interp-lerp-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.98,
      "size": 31680,
      "text": "正是这一步插值，让锯齿状的格子变成了顺滑的曲线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "marching-squares",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/marching-squares/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.76,
      "size": 28224,
      "text": "拖动阈值滑块，看等高线随高度层层收缩。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "marching-squares",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/marching-squares/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.38,
      "size": 38160,
      "text": "阈值越高，曲线越贴近山峰，把两座高斯峰勾勒得清清楚楚。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "marching-squares",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/marching-squares/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.07,
      "size": 33120,
      "text": "行进方块：逐格判断四角，查表连边，插值定点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "marching-squares",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/marching-squares/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.08,
      "size": 33264,
      "text": "地形等高线、气象等压线、医学等值面，背后都是它。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "marching-squares",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
